Hostname: notshubham.com



6️⃣ Point Your GoDaddy Domain to Your VPS
Log in to GoDaddy.
Go to My Products > Domains > notshubham.com.
Click on DNS Management.
Find the A Record for @ and update it with your VPS IP.
Add a CNAME record:
Name: www
Value: notshubham.com
Wait a few minutes to a few hours for the DNS to update.


